### Authenticated Session (token required)
POST http://localhost:3000/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": 1,
  "score": 100,
  "durationSeconds": 120,
  "metadata": {
    "level": "easy",
    "platform": "web"
  }
}

### Guest Session
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/game-sessions/guest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": 1,
  "score": 80,
  "durationSeconds": 90,
  "metadata": {
    "level": "easy",
    "platform": "mobile"
  }
}